  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Single-center study in order to assess whether the tap block can make extremely beneficial
      in terms of reducing the acute and chronic pain as well as for use of opioids and side
      effects related to it in patients undergoing surgery to minimally invasive partial
      nephrectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
